# Mobile Product Page for Laku Ecommerce

## OBJECTIVE
Create a comprehensive, mobile-first product detail page at `/product/[id]` route optimized for mobile devices (320px - 767px).

## TARGET ROUTE
`http://localhost:3000/product/[id]`

## TARGET DEVICES
- Mobile phones: 320px - 767px width
- Portrait orientation primary
- Touch-optimized interactions

## IMPORTANT DESIGN PHILOSOPHY
- **DO NOT specify exact colors** - Choose colors that create excellent contrast for readability, match the Laku brand aesthetic, and follow modern ecommerce best practices
- Use appropriate accent colors for CTAs, sale badges, and interactive elements
- Ensure all text is readable over product images and backgrounds
- Touch targets minimum 44x44px
- Thumb-friendly bottom navigation

---

## ðŸ“± MOBILE PAGE STRUCTURE

### 1. HEADER INTEGRATION (USE EXISTING)
**DO NOT create a new header** - Use the existing Laku mobile header:
- Your current search bar: "Cari di LAKU..." with camera icon
- Keep existing header height and styling
- Product page content starts below the existing header

**Product-Specific Header Actions:**
- Add these to your existing header component:
  - Back button (left) - navigate to previous page
  - Share icon (if not already present)
- Keep existing: Search bar, Camera icon

**Note**: The header component already exists in your layout - just enhance it with back button for product page context

### 2. PRODUCT IMAGE CAROUSEL
**Full-width swipeable gallery:**
- Height: 80-90vw (roughly square)
- Swipe gestures enabled
- Snap to each image
- Image counter overlay (e.g., "1/4") - top right corner
- Dot indicators at bottom (optional)
- Double-tap to zoom
- Pinch to zoom
- Smooth transitions between images
- Preload next/previous images

### 3. PRODUCT INFO SECTION
**Price Display:**
- Current sale price: Large (28-32px), bold, prominent color
- Original price: Medium (16-18px), struck through, grayed
- Discount badge: Pill shape, percentage (e.g., "-50%")
- Currency symbol displayed
- Padding: 16px horizontal

**Product Title:**
- Font size: 18-20px
- Font weight: Bold
- Line clamp: 2-3 lines max
- Color: Dark/primary text
- Padding: 16px horizontal

**Badges Row:**
- Seller/store badge (if trending)
- "Trends Store" badge
- Other promotional badges
- Horizontal scroll if too many

**Quick Info Tags:**
- Brief descriptor pills (e.g., "Casual", "Loose Fit", "Winter")
- Horizontal scroll
- Small, subtle styling

### 4. VARIANT SELECTION
**Size Selector:**
- Label: "Size" with selected value shown
- Button grid: 4 columns
- Each size button: Pill shaped, outlined
- Selected state: Filled background, bold border
- Out of stock: Disabled appearance, diagonal line
- Touch target: 44px minimum height
- Spacing between buttons: 8-12px

**Action Links Row:**
- "Size Guide" link with icon
- "Check My Size" link with icon
- "Not your size? Tell me your size" helper

**Color Selector** (if applicable):
- Label: "Color" with selected name
- Horizontal scroll of color swatches
- Each swatch: 48-56px circle or square
- Selected: Bold border ring
- Image thumbnails if colors have patterns

**Quantity Selector:**
- Label: "Quantity"
- Minus button | Number display | Plus button
- Centered layout
- Large touch targets (44px)
- Min: 1, Max: stock available

### 5. SHIPPING & DELIVERY CARD
**White card with border/shadow:**
- Icon on left (truck/shipping)
- Text layout:
  - "Shipping to [Country/Region]"
  - Shipping method badge (e.g., "Free Shipping")
  - Estimated delivery: "Jan 23 - Jan 28"
- Chevron right to expand details
- Tap to see full shipping info modal

### 6. POLICIES CARDS
**Each card expandable:**

**COD Policy Card:**
- Icon + "COD Policy"
- Brief description
- Chevron to expand

**Return Policy Card:**
- Icon + "Return Policy"  
- Brief text (e.g., "Free Return")
- Chevron to expand

**Shopping Security Card:**
- Shield icon + "Shopping Security"
- Bullet points: "Safe Payments", "Privacy Protection"
- Chevron to expand

### 7. SELLER CARD
**Prominent card with padding:**
- Seller logo/avatar (left, 48-56px circle)
- Seller name with verification badge
- Star rating (small stars) + followers count
- Stats row:
  - "500K+ Sold Recently" with fire icon
  - "99K+ Repurchase" with repeat icon
- "Trends Store" badge if applicable
- Action buttons (full width):
  - "Follow" button (outlined)
  - "All Items" button (filled)

### 8. SELLER OTHER PRODUCTS
**Horizontal scroll section:**
- Section title: "More from this seller"
- Horizontal scroll (no pagination)
- Each product card:
  - Square image
  - Product name (truncated)
  - Price
  - Small discount badge if applicable
- 4-6 products visible with scroll

### 9. TAB NAVIGATION
**Sticky horizontal tabs (stick below header on scroll):**
- Three tabs: "Goods" | "Details" | "Recommend"
- Full width, equal distribution
- Active tab: Underlined with accent color
- Smooth scroll to tab content
- Background matches page

### 10. GOODS TAB CONTENT (DEFAULT)
Shows sections 3-8 above in order.

### 11. DETAILS TAB CONTENT
**When Details tab is active:**

**Model Information Card:**
- Model avatar (circular, 40px)
- "Model is wearing: S"
- Measurements: Height, Bust, Waist, Hips
- Small text, grid layout

**Product Specifications:**
- Table or list format
- Rows: Material, Season, Style, Fit, Closure, etc.
- Label: Value pairs
- Alternating row backgrounds for readability

**Description Section:**
- Expandable "View more" if long
- Body text, readable size (14-15px)
- Line height: 1.6
- Feature bullet points if applicable

**Size Chart:**
- Table with horizontal scroll
- Columns: Size | Foot Length (cm)
- Recommended size highlighted
- Helper text: "Based on your measurements, size 40"

**Customer Size Reference:**
- "Buyers' size feedback" title
- Sample data showing what other customers bought
- Usernames + their size choices
- Foot length + size purchased

### 12. REVIEWS SECTION (IN DETAILS TAB)
**Rating Summary Card:**
- Large rating number (e.g., 4.55)
- 5 stars display
- Total review count
- Review policy info icon

**Fit Breakdown:**
- Horizontal bars showing distribution
- Small | True to Size | Large
- Percentages displayed

**Filter/Sort Bar:**
- "All Reviews" button (shows count)
- "Image" filter button
- Sort dropdown (Most Recent, Highest Rating, etc.)

**Filter Tags:**
- Horizontal scroll chips
- "No Smell", "Good Portability", "Keep Warm", etc.
- Tap to filter reviews
- Active state clearly shown

**Review Cards:**
- User avatar + masked username
- Star rating (5 stars)
- Date posted
- Product variant info (Color, Size)
- Review text (expandable if long)
- "Translate" link if foreign language
- Review images (if attached) - horizontal scroll
- "Helpful" button with count
- Verified purchase badge
- Points program indicator if applicable

**Load More:**
- Button at bottom to load more reviews
- Or infinite scroll (auto-load)

### 13. RECOMMEND TAB CONTENT
**Category Filter Pills:**
- Horizontal scroll
- "Recommend" | "Underwear & Sleepwear" | "Apparel Accessories"
- Active pill highlighted

**"You May Also Like" Section:**
- Grid layout: 2 columns
- Product cards:
  - Image (aspect ratio 3:4)
  - Seller badge (if trends)
  - Product name (2 line truncate)
  - Current price (bold)
  - Original price (struck through) if on sale
  - Discount percentage badge
  - Sales count (e.g., "100+ sold")
  - "#3 Bestseller in [Category]" badge if applicable
  - Quick cart button (bottom-right circle)

**Matching Styles Section:**
- Title: "Matching Styles"
- Horizontal scroll
- Larger cards showing styled outfits
- Item count per style set

**Load More:**
- "View More" button at bottom
- Loads additional products or navigates to category

### 14. BOTTOM NAVIGATION (USE EXISTING + PRODUCT ACTIONS)

**Important**: Your app already has a bottom navigation with:
- Beranda (Home)
- Video  
- Pesan (Messages)
- Keranjang (Cart) - with badge
- Profil (Profile)

**For Product Page - Two Options:**

**Option A: Overlay Action Bar (Recommended)**
Create a **sticky action bar** that sits ABOVE your existing bottom nav:
- **Height**: 56-60px
- **Position**: Fixed, sits above bottom nav (bottom: 56px)
- **Background**: White with top shadow
- **Layout**: Horizontal split
  - Left (30%): Wishlist heart icon + label
  - Right (70%): "Add to Cart" button (with discount if applicable)
- **This doesn't replace your bottom nav** - it's an additional layer

**Option B: Contextual Bottom Nav**
On product pages, temporarily replace bottom nav with product actions:
- Store icon | Wishlist | Add to Cart (60% width)
- When user scrolls up, show regular bottom nav
- When viewing product, show product actions

**Recommended: Use Option A** to maintain navigation consistency

