## ðŸŽ¨ MOBILE VISUAL DESIGN

### DESIGN CONSISTENCY WITH LAKU
**Match your existing design system:**

**Current Laku Design Patterns (from your screenshots):**
- **Price Color**: Red (Rp in red) - use for sale/current price
- **Original Price**: Gray, struck through (smaller text)
- **Sold Count**: Gray text, format: "X+ terjual"
- **Product Cards**: White background, rounded corners, subtle shadow or border
- **Product Images**: Rounded corners, consistent aspect ratio
- **Spacing**: Clean, generous whitespace
- **Typography**: Clean sans-serif, good hierarchy

**Apply These to Product Page:**
- Use the same red color for product price
- Same typography scale and font family
- Same card styling (shadows, borders, radius)
- Same spacing patterns
- Consistent button styles with your existing UI

### Typography
- Product title: Bold, 18-20px
- Price: Bold, 28-32px
- Original price: 16px, strike-through
- Body text: 14-15px
- Small labels: 12-13px
- Button text: 15-16px, semi-bold

### Spacing
- Page padding: 16px horizontal
- Section spacing: 24px vertical
- Card padding: 16px
- Element spacing: 12px

### Touch Targets
- Minimum: 44x44px
- Buttons: 48px height preferred
- Icon buttons: 44x44px minimum
- Spacing between tappable elements: 8px minimum

### Cards & Containers
- Border radius: 8-12px
- Box shadow: Subtle (0 2px 8px rgba)
- Border: 1px solid if not using shadow
- Background: White or very light

### Interactive States
- **Default**: Defined styling
- **Hover**: N/A (touch device)
- **Active/Pressed**: Slight scale down (0.95-0.98), opacity change
- **Disabled**: 50% opacity, no interaction
- **Loading**: Spinner or skeleton

### Animations
- Transitions: 200-300ms ease
- Page transitions: Slide in from right
- Modal entry: Slide up from bottom
- Toast notifications: Slide down from top

---

## ðŸ”§ MOBILE FUNCTIONALITY

### Image Gallery
- Swipe gesture support (left/right)
- Snap to each image
- Pinch to zoom
- Double-tap to zoom
- Smooth transitions
- Image counter updates

### Variant Selection
- Size button tap: Select size, update selection
- Out of stock: Cannot select, visual feedback
- Quantity: +/- buttons, number validation
- Color: Tap to select, show selection state

### Add to Cart
- Tap button: Validate selections
- If no size selected: Prompt to select
- Show loading state (spinner in button)
- Success: Toast notification
- Update cart badge count
- Option: Continue shopping or go to cart

### Wishlist/Save
- Tap heart: Toggle saved state
- Animation: Heart fills/empties
- Persist across sessions
- Require login if not authenticated
- Feedback: Toast or icon animation

### Tab Navigation
- Tap tab: Activate tab
- Smooth scroll to content
- Highlight active tab
- Lazy load tab content if needed

### Review Interactions
- Tap review card: Expand if truncated
- Tap review images: Open gallery viewer
- Tap "Helpful": Increment count, visual feedback
- Filter tags: Toggle active state
- Sort dropdown: Show bottom sheet options

### Modals & Bottom Sheets
- Size guide: Slide up from bottom
- Shipping details: Slide up from bottom
- Policy details: Slide up from bottom
- Dismiss: Swipe down or tap backdrop

### Scroll Behavior
- Header: Fixed at top
- Tabs: Sticky below header on scroll
- Bottom bar: Always fixed
- Smooth scroll to sections

---

## ðŸ“Š MOBILE DATA STRUCTURE

### Product Object
```typescript
{
  id: string
  name: string
  description: string
  price: number
  originalPrice: number
  discount: number
  currency: string
  rating: number
  reviewCount: number
  images: string[]
  variants: {
    sizes: { value: string, inStock: boolean }[]
    colors: { name: string, hex?: string, image?: string }[]
  }
  stock: number
  seller: {
    id: string
    name: string
    logo: string
    verified: boolean
    rating: number
    followers: number
    soldCount: string
    repurchaseRate: string
    isTrending: boolean
  }
  shipping: {
    destination: string
    method: string
    free: boolean
    estimatedDelivery: string
  }
  specifications: Record<string, string>
  sizeChart: SizeChartData
}
```

