## ðŸŽ¨ COLOR SCHEME GUIDANCE

Choose colors that:
- Make price highly visible and attention-grabbing
- Create clear distinction between primary and secondary actions
- Ensure bottom bar stands out from page content
- Make sale/discount badges pop without being jarish
- Provide excellent readability for all text sizes
- Work well for success states (cart add, save)
- Match Laku brand identity

